## Env keys

Use **`slipiq_env.py`** — same names as `.env.example` (`PARLAY_API_KEY`, `ODDS_API_KEY`/`ODDS_API_2`/`ODDS_API_3`, `DISCORD_DAILY_PICKS_CHANNEL`, `CHANNEL_TEAM_PARLAY`, `TOMORROW_IO_API_KEY`, etc.). Do not add new env names without updating `slipiq_env.py`.
